(119, 1, '2015-10-21 12:34:39', '2015-10-21 09:34:39', 'Advertise, Market and Promote your business with The Danbury Titans this season!\r\n\r\nThere is no better, more cost effective way to locally promote your business or product than by utilizing arena advertising to reach engaged, passionate fans and consumers.\r\n\r\nThe Danbury Ice Arena is a 2,300 seat multi-purpose arena located in the heart of Danbury, CT with 750,000 visitors annually.\r\n\r\nThe Danbury Titans and Danbury Ice Arena play an integral role as a key family entertainment destination for the greater Danbury, Fairfield County, Putnam County, Westchester County and Dutchess County communities.\r\n\r\n·         Danbury Ice Arena attracts an average 750,000 patrons per year\r\n\r\n·         55% male 45% female\r\n\r\n·         Two thirds of visitors are in the prime advertising demographic of 25-54 years old\r\n\r\n·         88% of arena attendees have an annual income of $50,000 or more\r\n\r\n·         The venue offers year-round exposure for advertisers to promote brand messaging to local, active consumers\r\n\r\n<strong>Advertising opportunities include:</strong>\r\n\r\nScoreboard signage, rink board (dasher board) signage, banners and back lit signage, penalty box and player bench sponsorship signage, on site booth space, wall decals, arena foyer and locker room signage plus online and local radio opportunities\r\n\r\nTo discuss a custom sponsorship package please contact:\r\n\r\n<strong>Jed Wilson\r\nVice President of Corporate sponsorships</strong>\r\n<a href="mailto:j.wilson@danburytitans.com">j.wilson@danburytitans.com</a>', 'Become a sponsor', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-21 12:34:39', '2015-10-21 09:34:39', '', 16, 'http://test/2015/10/21/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
